    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 12. H. minuta sp. n. (3 – head, 4 – 6 – eunomy of pronotum and hemelytra in female, 7, 8 – paramere, 9 – parandria, 10 – aedeagus, 11 – median endosomal sclerite, 12 – pregenital plate of female)." ;
